title: Nahal Qanah cave
description: Cave in western Samaria containing archaeological traces from the Pottery Neolithic period (Yarmukian culture), the Chalcolithic Period, and the Early Bronze Age.

properties.description: Point representing the approximate imagery location of the entrance to the Nahal Qanah cave, after Gopher 1996.
properties.title: Approximate imagery location of Nahal Qanah cave
